{
  "id": "gen-neon-acid-geometry",
  "name": "Neon Acid Geometry",
  "category": "generative",
  "url": "shaders/gen-neon-acid-geometry.wgsl",
  "description": "Geometric shapes (triangles, hexagons, circles) morphing and melting in psychedelic neon. Upgraded with universal-indicator pH color science: geometry edges glow with realistic acid/base transitions driven by bass oscillation. Critical-angle refraction distortion, temporal feedback trails, chromatic aberration, and ACES tone mapping.",
